Add the LCD controller layer definition and descriptor structure for
sam9x75 for the following layers,
- Base Layer
- Overlay1 Layer
- Overlay2 Layer
- High End Overlay

Signed-off-by: Manikandan Muralidharan <manikandan.m@microchip.com>
